{"tid":2060120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新入職及現職中小學教師新學年起須接受培訓","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T12:35:50.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aed7b3cec49f2824517ebe7ed56788fccf58da2a","tid":2060120,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531503-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531503-20200611.htm&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=91b8980a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531503-20200611.htm&h=b96badb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531503-20200611.htm</a>"},{"pid":"75fc319e35249a6d79870b20cf3d2f130464364f","tid":2060120,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"新學年起，教育局要求新入職及現職中小學教師接受培訓。<strong>其中新入職教師要在3年內完成30小時由教育局提供的核心培訓課程，涉及價值觀、操守、國家及國際教育發展等。教師要晉升，要在5年內修畢90或130小時課程，視乎晉升職級。</strong><br />\n<br />\n教聯會認為安排合理；教協質疑，教育局有政治動機。"},{"pid":"68f5d2fa4373bd9405b85d899e6cdedc95170198","tid":2060120,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"其中新入職教師要在3年內完成30小時由教育局提供的核心培訓課程，涉及價值觀、操守、國家及國際教育發展等。教師要晉升，要在5年內修畢90或130小時課程，視乎晉升職級。"},{"pid":"29b5a20f1801259ba5fb9e960277da600e9f039d","tid":2060120,"uid":298477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FC32VvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFC32VvL.png&h=cb2f703f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/circular/upload/edbc/EDBC20006C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fcircular%2Fupload%2Fedbc%